\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n價錢消費低<br />\n<br />\n包撚哂一個沙灘做private dinner 都係講緊三千港紙樓下埋單<br />\n<br />\n包車連司機十個鐘都係四百港紙<br />\n<br />\n風景唔差<br />\n<br />\nvilla 又比其他東南亞國家平"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:43:02.000Z","msg":"10個鐘 4舊水 堅平<br />\n有冇去過另外2個地方？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:57:53.000Z","msg":"無<br />\n不過聽講蘇梅消費較高，機票酒店都係<br />\n<br />\n長灘島完全無留意"},{"pid":"d991424eece25c7de3556dd2cf4a8dbcefefe920","tid":739481,"uid":184827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:00:14.000Z","msg":"峇里島<br />\n<br />\n如果想玩潛水就有Mola mola睇<br />\n<br />\n其他就5知"},{"pid":"f6640fcd39023e787a8af569b5bbd4fa74aecd20","tid":739481,"uid":166595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ce3ea053b4cd99718f26086c2e606daff8df74b","tid":739481,"uid":176306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:56:20.000Z","msg":"認真 6-7日會悶死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求其一個島去3日都夠 resort入面玩都好d 試過包車去出面就係農村<br />\n印尼玩水上項目貴過泰國好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:00:14.000Z","msg":"我都驚冇野玩（唔識游水）預浮潛 陽光海灘<br />\n<br />\n因為去度蜜月 所以預去一星期 <br />\n<br />\n我見蘇梅2個人洗費3萬 東南亞黎講有d貴"},{"pid":"c61c887038d418aa4297627a0530ed5792531409","tid":739481,"uid":166595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d991424eece25c7de3556dd2cf4a8dbcefefe920","tid":739481,"uid":184827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:00:14.000Z","msg":"峇里島<br />\n<br />\n如果想玩潛水就有Mola mola睇<br />\n<br />\n其他就5知"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:02:19.000Z","msg":"翻車魚？ 岩岩上網睇好大條"},{"pid":"d5ac6080cd37e07c20b99ec86411752e1ed84d4a","tid":739481,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:13:45.000Z","msg":"你想玩乜？<br />\n我只去過峇里同蘇梅<br />\n峇里唔太掂，景冇蘇梅咁好，如果你只留喺酒店唔出去，建議你住東南邊嘅酒